    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300068802_6_4647-4717",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "4647-4717",
      "markText": "从此河套永远受着鞑靼骑士的蹂躏，却葬送了一个内阁大学士、一个总督陕西三边军务。严嵩复为首辅，再在那半清客、半权臣的局面下，维持十五年的政权。",
      "totalCount": 392,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300068802&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=4647&rangeEnd=4717",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/76832f10813ab8160g01281f?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=4647&rangeEnd=4717"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300068802_6_7495-7548",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "7495-7548",
      "markText": "蜗牛的触角伸出了，但是觉得空气不利，终于还是收回，居正只是再埋头于朝章国故的探索，对于时政，便不更置一辞。",
      "totalCount": 315,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300068802&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=7495&rangeEnd=7548",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/76832f10813ab8160g01281f?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=7495&rangeEnd=7548"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300068802_4_1419-1446",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "1419-1446",
      "markText": "佛家所谓“阅尽他宝，终非己分”，是一句颠扑不破的名言。",
      "totalCount": 306,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300068802&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=1419&rangeEnd=1446",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/76832f10813ab8160g01281f?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=1419&rangeEnd=1446"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300068802_6_9331-9393",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "9331-9393",
      "markText": "在太子的职位没有确定以前，裕王、景王成为急切的竞争者，幸亏他们都只是平庸到无可奈何的人物，所以宫廷以内，不曾演出流血的惨剧。",
      "totalCount": 306,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300068802&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=9331&rangeEnd=9393",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/76832f10813ab8160g01281f?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=9331&rangeEnd=9393"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300068802_10_5716-5770",
      "chapterUid": 10,
      "range": "5716-5770",
      "markText": "他又爱上姑母的女儿三娘子，把她娶了。事情应当满足了，不幸俺答也爱上他的外孙女，三娘子便转移到外祖父的怀抱里。",
      "totalCount": 289,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300068802&chapterUid=10&rangeStart=5716&rangeEnd=5770",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/76832f10813ab8160g01281f?chapterUid=10&rangeStart=5716&rangeEnd=5770"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300068802_5_7846-7908",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "7846-7908",
      "markText": "他认为十三岁的孩子就中举人，以后便会自满，反而把上进的志愿打消，这是对于居正的不利，因此主张趁此给他一些挫折，使他更能奋发。",
      "totalCount": 255,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300068802&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=7846&rangeEnd=7908",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/76832f10813ab8160g01281f?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=7846&rangeEnd=7908"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300068802_16_24309-24372",
      "chapterUid": 16,
      "range": "24309-24372",
      "markText": "季驯对于居正的感激，真是彻底，直到居正身后，全家被祸的时候，他还冒着神宗盛怒，上疏请求降恩宥释，终于季驯也得到革职为民的处分。",
